headline: Heavy Transportation Equipment Stocks Q3 Results: Benchmarking Wabash (NYSE:WNC)
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Wabash (NYSE:WNC) and the rest of the heavy transportation equipment stocks fared in Q3.
